Resource Profile: openIMIS Policy Holder Organization

Official URL: https://github.com/openimis/openimis_fhir_r5_ig/StructureDefinition/openimis-policy-holder-organization Version: 0.1.0
Draft as of 2025-08-26 Computable Name: OpenIMISPolicyHolderOrganization

Defines an Organization for openIMIS which maps to a Policy Holder under Formal Sector scheme.

Usages:

  • Refer to this Profile: openIMIS Contract
  • Examples for this Profile: My Trade
  • CapabilityStatements using this Profile: openIMIS Capability Statement

You can also check for usages in the FHIR IG Statistics
